abstract: Dalai Lama cancels scheduled appearances in United States after doctors at Mayo Clinic in Minneapolis advise him to return to India to rest.
lead_paragraph: The Dalai Lama canceled appearances in the United States after a checkup at the Mayo Clinic in Minneapolis and planned to return to India to rest, the University of Colorado and the Tibetan Association of Colorado said Friday.
